text: The 2024-25 FC Red Bull Salzburg season is the 92nd season in the existence of FC Red Bull Salzburg and the club's 35th consecutive season in the top league of Austrian football. Salzburg also participated in this season's editions of the Austrian Cup. They finished again as runner-up in the league. ==Squad== * Goalkeepers: 24 Alexander Schlager, 92 Salko Hamzic, 1 Janis Blaswich * Defenders: 3 Aleksa Terzic, 4 Hendry Blank, 5 Bryan Okoh, 6 Samson Baidoo, 29 Daouda Guindo, 39 Leandro Morgalla, 36 John Mellberg, 23 Joane Gadou, 2 Maximiliano Caufriez * Midfielders: 14 Maurits Kjaergaard, 15 Mamady Diambou, 30 Oscar Gloukh, 18 Mads Bidstrup, 16 Takumu Kawamura, 7 Nicolas Capaldo, 49 Moussa Yeo, 10 Bobby Clark, 25 Oliver Lukic * Forwards: 9 Karim Onisiwo, 11 Yorbe Vertessen, 19 Karim Konate, 21 Petar Ratkov, 45 Dorgeles Nene , 28 Adam Daghim, 20 Edmund Baidoo, 81 Gaoussou Diakité * Coaching staff: Thomas Letsch (Coach), Onur Cinel, Vitor Matos (Assistance coaches), Eddie Gustafsson, Pedro Pereira (Goalkeeper coaches) ===Matches initial round=== ===Matches Champion group=== == Champions League qualification == == Champions League == ===Home === ===Away === ==UEFA Youth League == === Home=== === Away=== ==Table League phase == Pl.
